# Frontend environment (optional)
# Copy to .env and adjust when running locally (npm run dev).
#
# Leave unset to use: http://<hostname>:8000/api
# Or set to your backend API base, e.g.:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
#
# When using Docker, the image is built with VITE_API_URL=/api (same-origin).
